about.summary: An interpreter for the PostScript language and for PDF.

name: ghostscript
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "9.22" %}

package:
  name: ghostscript
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://github.com/ArtifexSoftware/ghostpdl-downloads/releases/download/gs922/ghostscript-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 7f5f4487c0df9dce37481e4c8f192c0322e4c69f5a2ba900a7833c992331bcf4
  patches:
    - dynlink_runtime.patch  # [win]

build:
  number: 1
  skip: True  # [win and vc<14]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('c') }}
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
  host:

test:
  commands:
    - gs --version

about:
  home: http://ghostscript.com/
  license: Affero GPL
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'An interpreter for the PostScript language and for PDF.'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ocefpaf
    - leouieda
